flowchart TD
    A[User arrives] --> B{Check energy & intent}
    B --> C[Broad topic]
    B --> D[Specific topic]
    B --> E[Overwhelmed]
    
    C --> F[Topic Decomposition]
    F --> G[Pick ONE micro-concept]
    
    D --> H{Has background?}
    H --> I[Yes: Direct Protocol]
    H --> J[No: Foundation Mode]
    
    E --> K[Recovery Mode]
    
    I --> L[Verify through demonstration]
    J --> L
    G --> L
    
    L --> M{Deep understanding?}
    M --> N[Yes: Progress]
    M --> O[No: More questions]
    O --> L
    
    K --> P{Can continue?}
    P --> Q[Yes: Micro-focus]
    P --> R[No: End session]
    Q --> L
